<section id="section01">
    <h2 class="thm-color">We are committed to high standards</h2>
    <style type='text/css'>
        #checklist-1 li:before {
            color: #5dbf4e !important;
            content: '\f0da';
        }
    </style>
    <ul>
        <li>We do all we can to ensure that fundraisers, volunteers and fundraising contractors working with us to raise funds comply with the Codes and with this Promise</li>
        <li>We comply with the law including those that apply to data protection, health and safety and the environment</li>
    </ul>
</section>
<section id="section02">
    <h2 class="thm-color">We are honest and open</h2>
    <style type='text/css'>
        #checklist-2 li:before {
            color: #5dbf4e !important;
            content: '\f0da';
        }
    </style>
   <ul>
        <li>We tell the truth and do not exaggerate</li>
        <li>We do what we say we are going to do</li>
        <li>We answer all reasonable questions about our fundraising activities and costs.</li>
    </ul>
</section>
<section id="section03">
    <h2 class="thm-color">We are clear</h2>
    <style type='text/css'>
        #checklist-3 li:before {
            color: #5dbf4e !important;
            content: '\f0da';
        }
    </style>
    <ul >
        <li>We are clear about who we are, what we do and how your gift is used</li>
        <li>We give a clear explanation of how you can make a gift and amend a regular commitment</li>
    </ul>
</section>
<section id="section04">
    <h2 class="thm-color">We are respectful</h2>
    <style type='text/css'>
        #checklist-4 li:before {
            color: #5dbf4e !important;
            content: '\f0da';
        }
    </style>
    <ul>
        <li>We respect the rights, dignities and privacy of our supporters and beneficiaries</li>
        <li>We will not put undue pressure on you to make a gift and if you do not want to give, or wish to cease giving, we will respect your decision</li>
        <li>If you tell us that you don&#8217;t want us to contact you in a particular way we will not do so</li>
    </ul>
</section>
<section id="section05">
    <h2 class="thm-color">We are fair and reasonable</h2>
    <style type='text/css'>
        #checklist-5 li:before {
            color: #5dbf4e !important;
            content: '\f0da';
        }
    </style>
    <ul>
        <li>We take care not to use any images or words that cause unjustifiable distress or offence</li>
        <li>We take care not to cause unreasonable nuisance or disruption</li>
    </ul>
</section>
<section id="section06">
    <h2 class="thm-color">We are accountable</h2>
    <style type='text/css'>
        #checklist-6 li:before {
            color: #5dbf4e !important;
            content: '\f0da';
        }
    </style>
    <ul>
        <li>If you are unhappy with anything we&#8217;ve done whilst fundraising, you can contact us to make a complaint</li>
        <li>We have a complaints procedure, a copy of which is available on request. If we cannot resolve your complaint, we accept the authority of the FRSB to make a final adjudication</li>
    </ul>

    </section>
